  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Perpetual Treasuries extends suspension of business operations",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Monetary Board of the Central Bank of Sri Lanka has decided to further extend the suspension of business activities and activities by a primary dealer of Perpetual Treasuries Company for a period of six (06) months with effect from 05 July 2022 at 4.30 pm.",
        "According to the orders issued under the Registered Masses and Securities Ordinance and the Local Treasury Bills Ordinance, the Finance Board has taken this decision with the aim of furthering the investigations carried out by the Central Bank of Sri Lanka."
      ],
